09:22.440 --> 09:34.080
in some ways, and it's crucial in others. In the One Tree, the characters, the
Elohim, who consider themselves to be very godlike, if not God itself, one

09:34.080 --> 09:40.760
problem for them is that the crucial events are happening somewhere else. And
they think, I mean, obviously since we're crucial, if what's happening to you

09:40.760 --> 09:55.620
were really important, it would have been happening here instead of way over
