21:04.400 --> 21:14.120
tradition is simply the whole question of the difference in God's relationship
to man between the old covenant and the new covenant. The term covenant is used

21:14.120 --> 21:24.700
to refer to a relationship or a deal between God and man. One of the things
you'll notice in the first trilogy is that Covenants always trying to make deals

21:24.700 --> 21:35.600
with the land. I'll do this if you'll do that, or if you don't ask me to do
this, I won't ask you to do that sort of thing. Every deal that he makes seduces

21:35.600 --> 21:46.520
him a step further, but they always fail because he's using them as substitutes
